&gt;hit counter, visitor counter or web counter&lt;/a&gt; in classic squemorphic odometer style.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.maiatoday.net/p/welcome-you-are-visitor-number-12345/hitCounters.png"
width="768"
height="214"
srcset="https://www.maiatoday.net/p/welcome-you-are-visitor-number-12345/hitCounters_hu_61da322f15ab08b9.png 480w, https://www.maiatoday.net/p/welcome-you-are-visitor-number-12345/hitCounters_hu_7fde84bb4a0c3ec6.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="hit counters"
class="gallery-image"
